== Additional Files required to build and run ==
You need to add the files kafui.jar, Kindlet-2.0.jar, KindletBookletDRM-2.0.jar, KindletImplementation-2.0.jar, KindletSystemPlugins-2.0.jar and utilities.jar from your Kindle Touch to the lib/ directory. 

